\bustMoveTo[2, -100, 720, 30]\nc<Senpai>Congratulations on losing your virginity, Saki! This is your
greatest achievement since joining the company. A debut has
to be like this, right!

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Ugh, Senpai... that's terrible! An auction all of a sudden!
I wasn't mentally prepared at all!

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>(Ah, calming her down is such a hassle. But it's true that
she did her best this time...)

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Well, don't be so mad. I sold you for a high price, didn't
I? Weren't you moved by your love story with your ex?
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Moved? I was so shocked I nearly fainted!

\nc<Senpai>Feeling a bit better now? I'll have the lobby staff do the
cleaning, so go take a shower.
\nc<Senpai>We need to have dinner and then work overtime, right?

\nc<>Saki somehow managed to get up and staggered towards the
shower room...
